### Appropriate and edit config
Means: Copy, paste and edit the original &quot;Configuration&quot; instead of/before importing/scanning it:
```lang-java
@Configuration
class MyConfig { 
  // copy, paste &amp; edit original (com.third.party) Configuration (omit unwanted parts/beans)
} // &lt;- use this
